DestroyModuleConfig EventNameBrowser:*
*EventNameBrowser: Cmd Function
*EventNameBrowser: add_window BrowserSaveName
*EventNameBrowser: window_name BrowserChangeName

DestroyFunc BrowserChangeName
AddToFunc   BrowserChangeName
+ I Echo BrowserChangeName $[w.id] $[w.iconname] $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]
+ I ThisWindow ("firefox") BrowserUseName
+ I ThisWindow ("Brave-browser") BrowserUseName
+ I ThisWindow ("Google-chrome") BrowserUseName

DestroyFunc BrowserUseName
AddToFunc   BrowserUseName
+ I Echo BrowserUseName $[w.id] $[w.iconname] $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]
#Make sure infostore has the info for this window
+ I Test (!EnvIsSet $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]) Break
+ I WindowStyle TitleFormat %c $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]
+ I WindowStyle IconTitleFormat %c $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]
#+ I SetEnv Icontestname $[w.iconname]
#+ I Test (!EnvMatch Icontestname $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]) Echo one: $[w.iconname]
#+ I Test (!EnvMatch Icontestname $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]) Echo two: $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]
#+ I Test (!EnvMatch Icontestname $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]) WindowStyle IconTitleFormat %c $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]
#+ I UnsetEnv Icontestname


DestroyFunc BrowserSaveName
AddToFunc   BrowserSaveName
+ I Echo BrowserSaveName $[w.id] $[w.iconname] $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]
+ I ThisWindow ("firefox") BrowserDoSave
+ I ThisWindow ("Brave-browser") BrowserDoSave
+ I ThisWindow ("Google-chrome") BrowserDoSave

DestroyFunc BrowserDoSave
AddToFunc   BrowserDoSave
+ I Echo BrowserDoSave $[w.id] $[w.iconname] $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]
+ I InfoStoreAdd browsername-$[w.id] $[infostore.browserlaunch]
+ I WindowStyle TitleFormat %c $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]
+ I WindowStyle IconTitleFormat %c $[infostore.browsername-$[w.id]]

